What is Finacle App?
Finacle is a core banking product developed by the Indian corporation Infosys that provides universal digital banking functionality to banks.
It was developed with Java and C/C++ language. 
It is used by banks across 100 countries to serve over 1 billion customers. 
In the world, Finacle is one of the top 20 financial banking applications but in Nigeria, it is used by two-thirds of the Financial service companies.
